data.description: Make me move !!!! Complete remodel from top to bottom in 2023 and move in ready! All new windows,plumbing/pvc, electrical in 2014. All new flooring/paint and remodeled kitchen and huge bathroom 2014. New roof in 2014. New septic tanks in 2014 All appliances included. 3rd bedroom features heat and A/C and private entrance .  concrete patio in 2014. 2 car garage and shed in back . . Country living at it's best but close to town, shopping and major highways. Twinsburg Schools! Huge private wooded back yard .
